Our Features

Streamconnect is an one to one video calling platform with a distinct feature of dynamically playing background music based on the expression of the other participant. This platform can easily target visually impaired people who can understand the emotions of the other person through this platform.

Emotion Detection

This platform helps visually impaired people who can understand the emotions of the other person through this platform

Smart Messaging

any user can start a realtime chat with the other user during the video call session.

Text to Speech

The chat messages will be converted to speech. Any user can turn it off according to the need

How it Works ?

01  Tones are played to denote different emotions

02  Tone playing once denotes neutral emotion

03  Tone repeating twice denotes happy emotion

04  Tone repeating thrice denotes sad emotion

05  Tone repeating four times denotes angry emotion

06  Tone repeating five times denotes fearful emotion
